All Implemented Interfaces:
IHasAlternateNode, com.mobius.vdrapi.IHasAlternateSectionData, com.mobius.vdrapi.IHasConnectionState, IHasDescription, com.mobius.vdrapi.IHasInfoForCreatingPages, IHasSectionInfo, IListFactory, INode
public class TopicSectionNode
extends SectionNode
implements IHasAlternateNode, com.mobius.vdrapi.IHasAlternateSectionData, IHasDescription

A TopicSectionNode object represents a topic item report section found within a topic, and is created by a topic item report.

Note: TopicItemSection values are distinctive. They contain an ABSPG value in the section name that references the starting page of the topic item. When retrieving the page data for the first page, include the ABSPG value for page 1. When accessing page data for the second page, use the page header returned from the first getPage call, because the actual section ID for the second page may be different. For this reason, this class implements IHasAlternateNode.
